.</p><p>Сообщение остается на контроле до 08.06.2021.</p><p>Приложение : Акт УК.</p>","author_name":"Администрация Центрального района","performer":null,"response_performers":[{"id":3381,"name":"ОБЩЕСТВО С ОГРАНИЧЕННОЙ ОТВЕТСТВЕННОСТЬЮ \"ЖИЛКОМСЕРВИС № 1 ЦЕНТРАЛЬНОГО РАЙОНА\" (ИНН 7841384710)"}],"files":[],"photos":[{"id":18115630,"url":"/storage/2/f58a23d0-cc99-46f7-897c-4905c5a43da3.jpg","original_name":"IMG_20210309_101440.jpg","thumbnail":"/media/cache/79/be/79be95012ed925654117c89008c8966d.jpg","size":"3000x4000"}],"reject":null,"interim_date":"2021-06-08"},"meta":{"title":"Ответ","icon_text":"ПО","icon_title":"Промежуточный ответ","bg_color":"#E3F2FD","border_color":"#536DFE","status_font_color":"#FFFFFF","status_bg_color":"#A5D6A7","icon_bg_color":"#536DFE"},"content_type":28},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13298915","payload":{"id":13298915,"dt":"2021-03-07T19:14:25.548272","status_name":"Рассмотрение","status":3},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-clock-o","icon_bg_color":"#FCAA62"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.status","key":"changestatus_13292273","payload":{"id":13292273,"dt":"2021-03-06T11:13:27.013945","status_name":"Модерация","status":1},"meta":{"title":"Изменение статуса сообщения","bg_color":"#EEEEEE","icon":"fa-hand-paper-o","icon_bg_color":"#469ED3"},"content_type":30},{"widget":"public.petition","key":"petition_3604889","payload":{"id":3604889,"dt":"2021-03-06T11:13:26.892248","status_name":"Получен ответ","body":[{"text":"Краска / граффити на стене в арке дома возле мусорных баков","typeof":1}],"photos":[{"url":"/storage/1/b4f43633-aa12-4520-bab2-c166465e691a.jpeg","original_name":"1217C9E5-3D70-4861-AF7A-5F01F3036ECC-1583-000000D48D6066BA.jpeg","id":4079061,"thumbnail":"/media/cache/b3/54/b35434b5037edd0b7b10015aa59e3988.jpg","original_url":"/storage/1/b4f43633-aa12-4520-bab2-c166465e691a.jpeg","size":"1536x2048"},{"url":"/storage/1/dbbc6f0c-87f4-4fc0-b61f-f8868ea03e8e.jpeg","ori